Quickstrike:




Quickstrike kept kicking at the door. He stopped after a while, and turned 
his head to Black Arachnia. For the first time in his life, he asked for 
help. "Do somethin'," he said. He even felt stupid saying it. "Ah heard that 
bot in forest!" He turned his head back to the door and kicked it a few more 
times. "Transulas, dang it! Open up!"
